The Denver Post Posted: 10/18/2015 10:51:52 AM MDT Aqib Talib (21) of the Denver Broncos tunes up before the first half of action at FirstEnergy Stadium. The Cleveland Browns hosted the Denver Broncos on Oct. 18, 2015. ( AAron Ontiveroz, The Denver Post )
